## Model File (.h3)

The trained deep learning model file is too large to be uploaded directly to GitHub.  
Therefore, it has been stored in Google Drive.

👉 Download Link: [Click here](https:https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1nUR9amhivOQ_AugO0RuqFV6dZtsMxcZo?usp=sharing

After downloading, place the file inside the `butterfly-app/` directory before running the project.
